properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 13 at 2:20AM MST until February 14 at 11:00AM MST by NWS Billings MT
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southwest winds gusting to 60 mph.

* WHERE...Livingston Area and Beartooth Foothills.

* WHEN...From 5 PM this afternoon to 11 AM MST Friday.

* IMPACTS...Strong crosswinds will make travel difficult along
Interstate 90 from Springdale through Livingston, and on local
roads near Nye.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Localized blowing snow is also possible.
Be alert for reduced visibility and snow-covered roads.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

Additional graphics for this hazard can be found at
http://www.weather.gov/billings

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 5 PM THIS AFTERNOON TO 11 AM MST FRIDAY
